gov.nih.nlm.meme.qa
Interface ITestSuite

All Superinterfaces:
Runnable
All Known Implementing Classes:
TestSuite
public interface ITestSuite
extends Runnable

Generically represents a test suite set. The set provides information about what it tests as well as implementing the actual validaiton check. Implementations of this class are Runnable.
